You have completed the tasks set to you by Uglash and earned the favour of War-tyrant Akúlhun.

'So you've found your way to the five corners of the Ettenmoors and think yourself a learned scout. Perhaps you are....

'Take this and know that using it will allow you to travel along paths we've discovered here that are safe and fast. Do not abuse this power.

'Aiding the towers, lumber-camp, mine, and central keep will earn you similar rewards over time. Some faster than others, but the trails are hard and taxing on the body and cannot be used often...

'Now...leave my sight, worm!'
Speak with War-tyrant Akúlhun at Gramsfoot.\n\nThe War-tyrant now has a gift to bestow upon you.
